s visible pretty quickly.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou do end up going to the broken bridge of Khazad-dum a few times.  The quest chain is clearly VERY INTERESTED in point out to you that SOMETHING HAPPENED there that might indeed be relevant to your interests.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs it happened, on the first quest driven visit to the location I hit level 60.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_133992\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_level60.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-133992\" data-attachment-id=\"133992\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/04/16/out-the-far-side-of-moria-and-into-lothlorien/mp12_level60/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_level60.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1771,897\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP12_Level60\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;The snowy tree graphic of a significant level or something\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_level60.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_level60.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_level60.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"304\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_level60.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_level60.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_level60.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_level60.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_level60.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-133992\"\u003eThe snowy tree graphic of a significant level or something\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSvanr there would bring me back again from the other side, getting there being super easy, barely an inconvenience, there being a path around maybe 200 meters to the north.  I marked up a map on a previous visit which I will now recycle.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_33885\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/moriaarrow.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-33885\" data-attachment-id=\"33885\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2013/08/22/on-the-far-side-of-moria/moriaarrow/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/moriaarrow.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"800,600\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MoriaArrow\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Chasm – Deep, wide, but not so long\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/moriaarrow.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/moriaarrow.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/moriaarrow.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/moriaarrow.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/moriaarrow.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/moriaarrow.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/moriaarrow.jpg?w=768 768w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/moriaarrow.jpg 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-33885\"\u003eChasm – Deep, wide, but not so long\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSo you go up to the top of that loop, do a few quests cleaning up dwarf trash and stray orc, hang out with Svanr a bit, then head for the First Hall and the exit.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEven there, however, Svanr has to guide you, and you do several farewell instance quests, first to go outside to see the sky in an instanced version of the Dimrell Dale, then you have to go back inside again.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_133985\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_onthewayout.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-133985\" data-attachment-id=\"133985\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/04/16/out-the-far-side-of-moria-and-into-lothlorien/mp12_onthewayout/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_onthewayout.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2314,1098\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP12_OnTheWayOut\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Svanr has another quest\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_onthewayout.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_onthewayout.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_onthewayout.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"285\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_onthewayout.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_onthewayout.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_onthewayout.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_onthewayout.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_onthewayout.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-133985\"\u003eSvanr has another quest\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThen you have to go BACK to the broken bridge at just to reinforce that SOMETHING HAPPENED there… and to re-use that Balrog model I showed you \u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/04/07/forochel-eregion-and-my-legendary-items/\"\u003ea couple of posts back\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_133990\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_gandalfreplay.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-133990\" data-attachment-id=\"133990\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/04/16/out-the-far-side-of-moria-and-into-lothlorien/mp12_gandalfreplay/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_gandalfreplay.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1950,900\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP12_GandalfReplay\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Are Gandalf and that Balrog old friends or something?\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_gandalfreplay.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_gandalfreplay.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_gandalfreplay.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"277\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_gandalfreplay.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_gandalfreplay.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_gandalfreplay.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_gandalfreplay.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_gandalfreplay.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-133990\"\u003eAre Gandalf and that Balrog old friends or something?\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eYou watch a bit of that and get an oddly worded message on your screen along the lines of “Did the fellowship come this way?  Or was that all the lingering effect of that orc blotter acid you had to clean up a couple zones back?”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThen you talk to the goat to end the whole thing… a sign that it might have been the blotter acid I think… and then Svanr has a couple of items to mention, some introductions give you to the quest givers outside, and then you’re done.  So I went forth into Lothlorien… and it was freaking night time.  The day/night cycle reasserts itself after about a week of it having no meaning.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_133987\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_lothatnight.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-133987\" data-attachment-id=\"133987\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/04/16/out-the-far-side-of-moria-and-into-lothlorien/mp12_lothatnight/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_lothatnight.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1351,626\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP12_LothAtNight\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Night again…\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_lothatnight.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_lothatnight.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_lothatnight.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"278\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_lothatnight.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_lothatnight.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_lothatnight.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_lothatnight.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_lothatnight.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-133987\"\u003eNight again…\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere were a number of alerts and updates and I gained a new title and I had an email from Galadriel, so well known as a chatty gossip who reaches out to random strangers.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_133984\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_emailfromgaladriel.png\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-133984\" data-attachment-id=\"133984\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/04/16/out-the-far-side-of-moria-and-into-lothlorien/mp12_emailfromgaladriel/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_emailfromgaladriel.png\" data-orig-size=\"534,278\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP12_EmailFromGaladriel\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;It says “Sent from my iPhone” at the bottom\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_emailfromgaladriel.png?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_emailfromgaladriel.png?w=534\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_emailfromgaladriel.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"534\" height=\"278\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_emailfromgaladriel.png 534w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_emailfromgaladriel.png?w=150\u0026amp;h=78 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_emailfromgaladriel.png?w=500\u0026amp;h=260 500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 534px) 100vw, 534px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-133984\"\u003eIt says “Sent from my iPhone” at the bottom\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBut those were all things to come.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAs for Moria, it went faster than I expected and wasn’t as grim as my memory had shaped it.  I managed to visit at least all the major encampments.  The stable master map shows I made a clean sweep of the place.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_134004\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_stablemastermapmoria.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-134004\" data-attachment-id=\"134004\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/04/16/out-the-far-side-of-moria-and-into-lothlorien/mp12_stablemastermapmoria/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_stablemastermapmoria.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1248,685\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP12_StableMasterMapMoria\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Stable Master map, post Moria\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_stablemastermapmoria.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_stablemastermapmoria.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_stablemastermapmoria.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"329\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_stablemastermapmoria.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_stablemastermapmoria.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_stablemastermapmoria.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_stablemastermapmoria.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_stablemastermapmoria.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-134004\"\u003eStable Master map, post Moria\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI did end up blowing a few mithril coins in the place.  Epic and sprawling though it is, it can be a bit of a maze and I was fine tossing a coin to get to the next stable master without having to blunder my way through another section or to get back to a quest giver as the end of an evening and bed time loomed.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAlong the way I also ended up getting the Busy Bee achievement, which comes from doing 300 daily tasks.  I am a firm believer in doing the daily tasks.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_133988\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_busybee.png\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-133988\" data-attachment-id=\"133988\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/04/16/out-the-far-side-of-moria-and-into-lothlorien/mp12_busybee/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_busybee.png\" data-orig-size=\"289,300\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP12_BusyBee\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;The busiest of bees\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_busybee.png?w=289\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_busybee.png?w=289\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_busybee.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"289\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_busybee.png 289w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_busybee.png?w=145\u0026amp;h=150 145w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 289px) 100vw, 289px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-133988\"\u003eThe busiest of bees\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThose deeds up the number of tasks you can do, so are a self-reinforcing cycle.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI also managed to get to kindred status with the Iron Garrison Guards.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_133989\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_ironguards.png\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-133989\" data-attachment-id=\"133989\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2025/04/16/out-the-far-side-of-moria-and-into-lothlorien/mp12_ironguards/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_ironguards.png\" data-orig-size=\"458,159\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;orientation\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MP12_IronGuards\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;Practically a guard myself now\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_ironguards.png?w=458\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_ironguards.png?w=458\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_ironguards.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"458\" height=\"159\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_ironguards.png 458w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/mp12_ironguards.png?w=150\u0026amp;h=52 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 458px) 100vw, 458px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-133989\"\u003ePractically a guard myself now\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThere are only two factions in Moria that I saw, the guards and the miners.  I am close to kindred with the miners.  A couple more days of daily tasks and I could clinch that.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAnd now Lothlorien lays before me.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv data-shortcode=\"caption\" id=\"attachment_33879\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/morialltheoutsidemap.jpg\"\u003e\u003cimg aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-33879\" data-attachment-id=\"33879\" data-permalink=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/2013/08/22/on-the-far-side-of-moria/morialltheoutsidemap/\" data-orig-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/morialltheoutsidemap.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"1582,1121\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{\u0026#34;aperture\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;credit\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;camera\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;caption\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;created_timestamp\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;copyright\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;focal_length\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;iso\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;shutter_speed\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;0\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;title\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;\u0026#34;}\" data-image-title=\"MoriaLLTheOutsideMap\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\u0026lt;p\u0026gt;To Lothlorien\u0026lt;/p\u0026gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/morialltheoutsidemap.jpg?w=500\" data-large-file=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/morialltheoutsidemap.jpg?w=600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/morialltheoutsidemap.jpg?w=600\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/morialltheoutsidemap.jpg?w=600 600w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/morialltheoutsidemap.jpg?w=1200 1200w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/morialltheoutsidemap.jpg?w=150 150w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/morialltheoutsidemap.jpg?w=500 500w, https://tagn.wordpress.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/morialltheoutsidemap.jpg?w=768 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp id=\"caption-attachment-33879\"\u003eTo Lothlorien… the old map… which is better frankly\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOutside, the first thing Svanr’s buddies set me to doing was killing orcs.  Same as it ever was.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI am still a ways from Mirkwood, but it is visible over the next hill, past Lothlorien.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
